name: Terima - PianoBulae Work #Q6
description:
"Terima" (Acceptance), sometimes is just a proof of maturity, that needs a lot of courage and bravery, not always a display of weakness and loss..

Piano Meets Granular Sampler in quarantine time. The Final part of a series entitled “PianoBulae Works”. Constructed entirely from fragments of a solo improvisation on an upright acoustic piano, recorded in 2016 and later manipulated on 2018 by granular sampler trough the eurorack system. 

All visuals are made in quarantine time
